datasets.name: dataset_17
queryLines: SELECT `Home Tile` AS `Home Tile`, MEASURE(`Unique Tile Views`) AS `Unique Tile Views`, MEASURE(`Unique Tile Clicks`) AS `Unique Tile Clicks`, MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Views`) AS `Unique Interstitial Views`, MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`) AS `Unique Interstitial Primary Button Clicks`, MEASURE(`Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`) AS `Unique Interstitial Secondary Button Clicks`, (MEASURE(`Unique Tile Clicks`) / MEASURE(`Unique Tile Views`)) * 100 AS `f_ctr` FROM `workspace.default.hpx_events_model_homepage_summary` ORDER BY `f_ctr` DESC
